emotes.msg: I no talk to you. You are not Drudge and I told not to talk to not Drudge!
Shanks gobbles the food in a happy dimwitted sort of way. He begins to babble about this and that.
Mmm! Slurp! Crunch! Munch! Those Biters think they special just because Klank give them blueprints to guard. Crunch! Munch! I could guard blueprints. No one gets nothing from me!
Shanks gobbles the food in a happy dimwitted sort of way. He begins to babble about this and that.
I named after my favorite food, Ursuin Shanks. So sweet meaty juicy! Do you have some?
Shanks gobbles the food in a happy dimwitted sort of way. He begins to babble about this and that.
This good, but you have any Meaties? They part of a balanced morning food. Those and apples.
Shanks gobbles the food in a happy dimwitted sort of way. He begins to babble about this and that.
I was one of first Drudges that learn to speak. My mother so proud. She call me "weeraawreee." That mean good smart son.
Shanks gobbles the food in a happy dimwitted sort of way. He begins to babble about this and that.
Mmm! This good! You have anymore? I not picky with food or drink. I like them all.
Shanks gobbles the food in a happy dimwitted sort of way. He begins to babble about this and that.
Chocolate makes me sick, but I love it. I don't blame chocolate for making me sick, it can't help it.`
